The main thing I want to get across is that someone can be sick and not “look sick”. You never know what someone else has going on. If you have any questions about my illness I would love to spread awareness to that as well!

I have an illness that not all would classify as an invisible illness because it can be more visible; however, my scars are covered a majority of the time so it is far less likely anyone would see them. I have hidradenitis suppurativa. I also have mental illness.

I wanted to take a moment to bring awareness to invisible illnesses. An invisible illness is any illness that you can not outright see on a person. There are many illnesses that can be classified as such. #illness #awareness #invisibleillness
